  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.megavoltcorp.com/">megavolt</a> - lead engineer
    </li>
    <li><a href="https://zerodev.app/">zerodev</a> - founding engineer</li>
    <li><a href="https://eternal.gg/">eternal.gg</a> - lead engineer</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="font-bold">Projects and Contributions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/turbo-eth/template-disco-app">turbo-eth</a> (ts)
      - disco and ceramic integrations for DID and VC gating
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/foundry-rs/forge-std/pull/270">forge-std</a> (sol)
      - forge cheatcode for solidity testing
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/hexcowboy/rslock">rslock</a> (rs) - a rust implementation
      of redis redlock
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Ahexcowboy+sort%3Acomments-desc"
        >cal.com</a
      > (ts) - web3 wallet integrations and token-gated meetings
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/hexcowboy/stetson">stetson</a> (rs) - a pure rust
      pubsub server
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/wagmi-dev/viem/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Ahexcowboy"
        >viem</a
      > (ts) - an ethereum interface library
    </li>
  </ul>
  <pre
    class="text-neutral-500">
//                   @
//                    )
//                   ( _m_
//                    \ " /,~~.
//                     `(''/.\)
//                      .&gt;' (_--,
//                   _=/d  . ^\
